window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>No man can win her heart - until now.... </p> <p>In the Gladium Province, the boundaries between humans and Morgons, the dragon-hybrid race, continue to blur as a new generation surrenders to long-forbidden temptation....</p> <p>Sorcha Linden does whatever she wants whenever she wants, and no one can stop her. Least of all a man. After all, they're good for only one thing - warming her bed. But then she meets Lorian Nightwing, brother of Lucius. Seductive and iron-willed, he is determined to melt her emotional defenses - and warm her rebellious heart. </p> <p>The beast within Lorian longs to cage Sorcha and mark her as his own. Forever. Yet the man within also longs to protect her. When a stalker starts leaving Sorcha suggestive gifts with cryptic messages bearing an ancient blood-cult symbol, Lorian's dragon side takes over. With her life at stake, Sorcha can no longer deny the love they share. </p> <p>But when evil tracks her into the night, will she be too late to claim it? </p> <p>Contains mature themes.</p>"; 
